title: "My Blog"
layout: "base.njk"
permalink: "blog/index.html"
---

<div class="blog-container">
  <div class="blog-intro">
    <p><strong>Hey, I’m Soumya Maheshwari, welcome to my learning pool.</strong></p>
    <p>This is where I post my raw thoughts, and dig into rabbit holes that make me curious. 
    Publishing here keeps me accountable — a small commitment to explore, research, and sometimes just think out loud.</p>
    <p>Most of what you’ll find here are seeds, ideas in progress — but I hope they span in something worthwhile over time.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="posts-list">
    {%- for post in collections.posts | reverse -%}
      <article class="post-preview">
        <a href="{{ post.url | url }}" class="post-link">
          <div class="post-header">
            <h2 class="post-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
            <time class="post-date">~ {{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          </div>
          <p class="post-description">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        </a>
      </article>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .blog-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px 20px 40px;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .blog-intro {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-family: 'SF Pro Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .blog-intro p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .posts-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .post-preview {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .post-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .post-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .post-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5em;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .post-title {
    font-family: 'SF Pro Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .post-description {
    font-family: 'SF Pro Display', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .post-date {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .post-title {
